                </p>

                <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Other help to buy a home</h2>
                <p class="govuk-body-l">
                    Please click here to
                    <a class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state govuk-!-font-weight-bold" id="eligible-result-find-a-provider-link" href="@Url.Action("Index", "Search")">find an organisation that sells shared ownership homes</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>




